1 contribution was made.
2 SECTION 2. The amendments to ORS 316.102 by section 1 of this 2026 Act apply to tax
3 years beginning on or after January 1, 2026, and before January 1, 2028.
4 SECTION 3. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the date on which the 2026
5 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative Assembly adjourns sine die.
